speaker.name: Rahul Jha
speaker.biography:
I'm a senior software engineer at https://deepsource.io, where I work on developing tools to improve code health and quality.

I'm the maintainer of [Vulture](https://github.com/jendrikseipp/vulture), and it will have your dead Python. Thank you!
